<div class="row">
        
        <div class="column column-12">
            <h1 class="board-title">Sitabani Forest Landscape</h1>
           
            <div class="row">
                <div class="column column-12">
                    <div class="board left-board icolumn icolumn-6" style="border:none !important; box-shadow: none !important;">
                        <h3>About The Sitabani Forest Landscape</h3>
                        <p style="background: #ebebeb; padding: 15px;">
                            Sitabani Forest Zone is also known as Corbett Landscape. Corbett Landscape is a beautiful tourist zone for visitors due to its 
                            fabulous attraction of river stream, floura and founa. Sitabani is now a part of Corbett Tiger Reserve. In this, Safari of Sitabani 
                            Landscape, you got a chance to spot a tiger, leopard, different species of deer such as barking deer, cheetal, sambhar and 
                            other species of animals. Sitabani is also a famous place for bird lovers, because various types of birds such as Emerald Dove,
                            White Bush Chat, Oriental Paid and more species found in this area.
                        </p>
                    </div>
