                        <h3>Safari Timings - Winter Season</h3>
                        <p>
                            07:00 AM to 10:00 AM (Morning Jeep Safari)<br/>
                            02:00 PM to 05:30 PM (Evening Jeep Safari)
                        </p>
                        <h3>Safari Timings - Summer Season</h3>
                        <p> 06:00 AM to 09:30 AM (Morning Jeep Safari)<br/>
                            03:00 PM to 06:30 PM (Evening Jeep Safari)
                    </div>
                    
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                <div class="column column-12">
                    <div class="board left-board icolumn icolumn-6" style="border:none !important; box-shadow: none !important;">
                        <h3>Booking Guidelines</h3>
                        <p>There are two types of booking in Corbett National Park<br/>
                            i) Day Visit Booking - (Morning : 06:00 AM to 10:00 AM), (Evening : 02:00 PM to 06:00 PM)<br/>
                            ii) Night Stay Booking (Dhikala, Bijrani, Durgadevi Only)<br/>
                            You need to follow these instructions before booking -<br/>
                            1. Allowed ID Proofs : Driving License, PAN Card, Voter ID, Passport, Student ID etc.<br/>
                            Note : You need to take the same ID Proof on your visit that is mentioned in your Booking Permit.<br/>
                            Note : Booking permit charges are non-refundable.<br/><br/>
                            2. Corbett Landscape allowes 6 persons maximum in single Gypsy.<br/>
                            3. All the facilities of Tourist Rest Houses are provided by forest department only.
                        </p>
                    </div>
